{"tid":2416957,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打，希望問銀行按揭利息計算問題","createTime":"2021-02-21T12:59:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T16:12:28.000Z","uid":90323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"30d03c92d92bced7eedc95eb5b8a10254d7f91e0","tid":2416957,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:59:00.000Z","msg":"我按恒新Morgage Link嘅，<br />\n上網人地話有87 定律咁去計還款息口，<br />\n我想問下，真實係點樣計每月還息口幾多，還幾多本金嘅?<br />\n<br />\nSay, 借左100萬，2厘<br />\n<br />\n恒新個還左幾多本金嘅計算遮遮掩掩咁，我懷疑佢用87定律收息。"},{"pid":"53f7861ed496feeaecc2c4a5c90a37304e305f07","tid":2416957,"uid":46286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"lm 學野， 我用 87 定律計唔返條數"},{"pid":"6835e690b6b79e676d20fa70368ae476225d10f3","tid":2416957,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53f7861ed496feeaecc2c4a5c90a37304e305f07","tid":2416957,"uid":46286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"lm 學野， 我用 87 定律計唔返條數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T13:03:42.000Z","msg":"印像中我用最簡單嘅計法，<br />\n例如當時欠100<br />\n2厘<br />\n100*2%/12<br />\n會大過實質佢每月收嘅利息(成年前中銀，唔肯定)，<br />\n如果係咁嘅前提，咁其實重按收rebate 係值得玩嘅。"},{"pid":"fcffad2f5b9ab8a88a383fbd53ccf37bcd0690b2","tid":2416957,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:04:02.000Z","msg":"例如， 今個月為例<br />\n<br />\n我還左9228, 佢由欠2512534 變成欠2506298<br />\n相減即我還左6236本金，<br />\n即我還左2992 息<br />\n<br />\n只係略為多於年息/12,<br />\n我1.4 厘<br />\n即 2512534*1.4/100/12<br />\n=2931"},{"pid":"1091fcddf48db38e97642bd6aed281e394b2c060","tid":2416957,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:10:26.000Z","msg":"用恆生按揭計算機，有表睇"},{"pid":"d96c792c4d3b943c9b140448b56e47189d8f9e25","tid":2416957,"uid":59100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T16:12:28.000Z","msg":"學野"}]}